#Helm 3 Installation

[vagrant@helmmaster software]$ curl -fsSL -o get_helm.sh https://raw.githubusercontent.com/helm/helm/master/scripts/get-helm-3

[vagrant@helmmaster software]$ chmod 700 get_helm.sh

[vagrant@helmmaster software]$ ./get_helm.sh

[vagrant@helmmaster software]$ helm repo add stable https://kubernetes-charts.storage.googleapis.com/

[vagrant@helmmaster software]$  helm repo update

The above command might take few minutes
